<% provide(:title, "Home") %>
<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-300 font-sans selection:bg-pink-900 selection:text-slate">
  <section class="relative border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 px-6 py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute left-[calc(50%-4rem)] top-10 -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl sm:left-[calc(50%-18rem)] sm:top-[-10rem]" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="aspect-1108/632 w-[69.25rem] bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-pink-600 opacity-20" style="clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-slate-400 sm:text-7xl">
        Zero Task,
        <span class="relative inline-block text-cyan-400">
          <span class="absolute inset-0 blur-sm text-cyan-500 opacity-70">Best Task.</span>
          <span class="relative">Best Task.</span>
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg font-medium text-slate-400 sm:text-xl/8 text-pretty">
        专注核心业务，告别繁琐配置。基于 Rails 8 Modern Monolith 架构，为您打造极简、高效的任务管理新范式。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 rounded border-2 border-cyan-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-400 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)] hover:bg-cyan-950/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(6,182,212,0.8)] transition duration-300">
          TASK.initialize()
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 group hover:text-slate transition">
          <span class="group-hover:text-pink-400">#</span> READ MORE
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
